headline: Qolab Concludes 2025 with Key Strategic Collaborations to Advance Quantum Hardware
summary: MADISON, Wis., December 23, 2025--Qolab closed 2025 with a series of strategic collaborations, product deployments, and industry leadership milestones that underscore growing momentum behind its approach to scalable superconducting quantum hardware. Together, these advances mark foundational progress toward the company’s mission to build a commercially useful quantum computer through semiconductor-aligned manufacturing and system-level integration.
